						               													<description>The super fun Fast Pace Words Card Game for the entire family.&amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#139;&amp;#10;Use your letter cards to build words and win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Content:&amp;#10;85 Playing Cards [each with 1 letter]&amp;#10;Rules and Game Variations&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players are dealt 5 cards each, 10 cards make a face-up stock pile, and the rest of the cards make the face-down draw pile. In a turn a player makes a word, if possible, using cards in their hand and the top of the stock pile; if they can, they keep all the cards of that word in a separate pile; the turn ends by drawing a card whether or not they made a word. The round ends when a player spells a word with the last stock card; the winner of the round is the player with the most cards won. The overall winner is the first player to win 3 rounds.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules for 10 different rules variants are included.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
